title: Sam Tinnesz - Lead Singer And Entrepreneur
itunes:title: Sam Tinnesz - Lead Singer And Entrepreneur
description:
The music industry is 90% business and 10% talent. And it’s not so much different from the internet marketing industry.
 
Sam Tinnesz is a music artist and entrepreneur with hit songs “Legends Are Made” & “Ready Set Let’s Go”.
 
Personally, I jam Sam’s music every morning at the gym. It has the underdog vibe to it that I resonate with.
 
In this interview, we talk about the business side of the music industry and how to create that buzz around your music, as well as monetizing.
 
Show Notes: https://underdogempowerment.com/sam-tinnesz/
